WEBVTT


00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.840
this is how Small the earth actually is

00:00:01.960 --> 00:00:03.360
compared to the rest of the solar system

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:04.600
check how Big Jupiter is

00:00:04.601 --> 00:00:06.081
the earth fits in it 1000 times

00:00:06.280 --> 00:00:07.000
when we zoom out

00:00:07.001 --> 00:00:09.081
we really see how gigantic the sun is

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:10.880
the Jupiter fits in it 1000 times

00:00:10.881 --> 00:00:12.561
and the earth even more than 1 million times

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:14.640
the sun is so big that 99

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:17.960
8% of all Solar System Mass comes from the Sun
